<%= "Dear #{@application.firstname} #{@application.lastname}," %>

We are pleased to inform you that you have been admitted into the <%= @enrollment.campyear %> Michigan Math and Science Scholars (MMSS) summer program at the University of Michigan in Ann Arbor!

To finalize your admission, please log in to <%= @url %> to accept or decline your admission.

<%= @offer_letter_text.html_safe %>

=======================================

YOUR PROGRAM ASSIGNMENTS
=======================================

Session Assignment:
<% @assigned_sessions.each do |as| %>
  • <%= as.camp_occurrence.display_name %>
<% end %>

Course Assignment:
<% @assigned_courses.each do |ac| %>
  • <%= ac.course.display_name %>
<% end %>

=======================================

IMPORTANT INFORMATION
=======================================

Response Deadline: <%= @enrollment.application_deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>

To accept or decline this offer, please visit your application at:
<%= @url %>

We look forward to your response.

Sincerely,
Michigan Math and Science Scholars Program
University of Michigan
